## Architecture Notes
- Next.js App Router with Turbopack
- Credits provider context in `components/credits-provider.tsx`
- History stored in browser localStorage (`lib/history-storage.ts`)
- `lib/uuid.ts` provides `generateId()` with fallback for non-secure (HTTP) contexts
- Remote dev access configured via `allowedDevOrigins` in `next.config.ts`
- `@tailwindcss/typography` used for prose styling on legal pages
